Python Package Updates
-----------------------

Requirements
-------------

sudo apt-get install python3-setuptools   |  Bunlardan emin değilim.  
sudo apt-get install python3-distutils    |  Ama yüklemekte zarar yok.

sudo apt-get install python3-pip

sudo apt-get install python3.6-dev

sudo apt-get install python3.7-dev

sudo apt install libgirepository1.0-dev

sudo apt-get install libpq-dev python-dev libxml2-dev libxslt1-dev libldap2-dev libsasl2-dev libffi-dev libcups2-dev libcairo2-dev

Packages
---------

sudo python3.7 -m pip install --ignore-installed asn1crypto certifi cffi chardet cryptography  defer distro-info httplib2 idna keyring keyrings.alt launchpadlib lazr.restfulclient lazr.uri louis macaroonbakery Mako MarkupSafe netifaces oauth olefile pexpect Pillow pip protobuf pycparser pycrypto pymacaroons PyNaCl pyRFC3339 python-dateutil python-debian pytz pyxdg PyYAML reportlab requests requests-unixsocket SecretStorage setuptools simplejson six urllib3 wadllib wheel zope.interface pycairo pycups pygobject --no-cache-dir
(... python3.7 ... kısmını python3 için de yapın.)
